{"tid":2135134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙豐9月起不再發行英國即期滙票","createTime":"2020-08-01T08:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T16:03:40.000Z","uid":291865,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"49fb71f4b5a3f3a7b015b213b953c8772f588fd7","tid":2135134,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"滙豐宣佈，自今年9月1日起，將不再發行在英國及法國兌付的任何貨幣即期滙票，建議客戶使用電滙方式處理滙款。滙豐表示，相關安排是基於業務及銀行產品檢視，並不時作出調整。<br />\n<br />\n大新銀行亦向客戶通知，自今年9月1日起，將暫停為客戶發出英鎊滙票服務，直至另行通知，公告未有解釋更新安排原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200801/RWFKJRQLS4EVGQWFB7Q45DG7AQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200801%2FRWFKJRQLS4EVGQWFB7Q45DG7AQ%2F&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=37335f46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200801%2FRWFKJRQLS4EVGQWFB7Q45DG7AQ%2F&h=e961ef99\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200801/RWFKJRQLS4EVGQWFB7Q45DG7AQ/</a>"},{"pid":"aae87ed71e328050ac0b116ee3266ddbd20135dc","tid":2135134,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a76a95f9c5f80233b8211581f88db8f8dfda53","tid":2135134,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:14:16.000Z","msg":"前幾日都見到，但好似對普通人無咩影響"},{"pid":"6f601dff17f68b67370fdb341d1786ecaee3e4d6","tid":2135134,"uid":201374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d0a76a95f9c5f80233b8211581f88db8f8dfda53","tid":2135134,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:14:16.000Z","msg":"前幾日都見到，但好似對普通人無咩影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"&quot;普通人&quot;都唔係主要收入來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55d033e4f86d9a16091e0d1bc9d1e46e161bb12","tid":2135134,"uid":105340,"like":0,"